hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Special Delivery hazelnut oil for natural hair The characteristic Turpin canvas gives an impression of brimming colour and lushness, as though the artist’s eye is right in the flower bed, hemmed in by diverse flora, with distant walls and hedges lending a sense of space and structure. While he claims to be vague on the names and details of particular species, there’s an instinctive feel for the different plant forms and the way they’ve been positioned by the gardeners.
